<div class="igColumns section">








<div class="cols-bg 
                    
                    bg-none
                    
                    
                    col-margin-bot
                    
                    
                    "
                    
                    >

        <div class="cols col-12">

        <div class="col col1 parsys"><div class="component-group parbase section">








<div class="component-group-wrapper outline">

    <div class="component-group-parsys js_component-group parsys"><div class="accordion parbase section">












<script>
    var i18n= i18n || {};
i18n['accordion.more']='\u986F\u793A\u8A73\u7D30';i18n['accordion.less']='\u4E0D\u986F\u793A';</script>

<div class="accordion-wrapper js_accordion accordion-expanded content"
     data-desktop="closed"
     data-mobile="closed"
     data-tablet="closed">
    
        
            
            
                <div tabindex="0" class="accordion-clickable js_accordion-clickable accordion-plus">
                    
                    <span class="accordion-text"><p>股票保證金</p>
</span>
                </div>
            
        
    
    
    <div class="accordion-parsys js_accordion_content accordion-content accordion-parsys parsys">
<!-- DBG: included_as_snippet=false -->
<div class="table section">






<script>
    PS.util.jspVars.set("removeTableProperties")(false);
</script>

<div class="responsive-table">

    <h3>股票保證金</h3>

<p>已設定非保證止損的差價合約倉位的保證金要求將以無止損情況下的保證金為上限（換言之若止損距離與當前價格相差較大，計算後保證金要求或會高於無止損情況下的保證金；若有此情況，保證金將會限制為相同倉位無止損情況下所需的保證金）。</p>

<table class="table-zebra-rows" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="1">
	<thead>
		<tr>
			<th scope="col" width="135"><p>&nbsp;</p>
			</th>
			<th scope="col" width="661">
			<h3>差價合約</h3>
			</th>
		</tr>
	</thead>
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td>
			<h3>無止損</h3>
			</td>
			<td><p><strong>股票股數x 每股價值x保證金價格比率</strong></p>

			<p>例：1000股Vodafone，每股價格為£1.94：</p>

			<p>1000 x 1.94 x 5% = £97保證金<br>
			&nbsp;</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>
			<h3>止損</h3>
			</td>
			<td><p><strong>(無止損倉位保證金 x 滑點指數) + 每點價值* x 止損距離</strong></p>

			<p>例：1000股Vodafone，每股價格為£1.94，非保證止損距離為3點：</p>

			<p>(£97 x 30% + (£10 x 3) = £59.10保證金</p>

			<p>* 注意： 100 英股 = £1 每點, 100 美股 = $1 每點，100 歐股= €1 每點。</p>

			<p>&nbsp;</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>
			<h3>保證止損</h3>
			</td>
			<td><p>以下兩個算式中<strong>較大值</strong>：</p>

			<p>1. 每點價值 X 止損距離（按點計算）+保證止損溢價</p>

			<p>2. 股票股數 x 股票價格 x 保證金率 (%)</p>

			<p>例：1000 股Vodafone，每股價格為 £1.94，保證止損距離為11點，保證止損溢價為0.3%：</p>

			<p>算式1：<span style="text-align: center;">(£10 x 11) + (1000 x £1.94 x 0.003) = £115.82 保證金</span></p>

			<p><span style="text-align: center;">算式2：1000 x £1.94 x 5% = £97 保證金</span></p>

			<p><span style="text-align: center;">因此保證金為£115.82，兩個算式結果中較大的值。</span></p>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>


    

</div>

</div>
</div>

    
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion parbase section">












<script>
    var i18n= i18n || {};
i18n['accordion.more']='\u986F\u793A\u8A73\u7D30';i18n['accordion.less']='\u4E0D\u986F\u793A';</script>

<div class="accordion-wrapper js_accordion accordion-expanded content"
     data-desktop="closed"
     data-mobile="closed"
     data-tablet="closed">
    
        
            
            
                <div tabindex="0" class="accordion-clickable js_accordion-clickable accordion-plus">
                    
                    <span class="accordion-text"><p>外匯保證金</p>
</span>
                </div>
            
        
    
    
    <div class="accordion-parsys js_accordion_content accordion-content accordion-parsys parsys">
<!-- DBG: included_as_snippet=false -->
<div class="table section">






<script>
    PS.util.jspVars.set("removeTableProperties")(false);
</script>

<div class="responsive-table">

    <h3>外匯差價合約保證金</h3>

<p>已設定非保證止損的差價合約倉位的保證金要求將以無止損情況下的保證金為上限（換言之若止損距離與當前價格相差較大，計算後保證金要求或會高於無止損情況下的保證金；若有此情況，保證金將會限制為相同倉位無止損情況下所需的保證金）。</p>

<table class="table-zebra-rows" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="1">
	<thead>
		<tr>
			<th scope="col" width="135"><p>&nbsp;</p>
			</th>
			<th scope="col" width="661">
			<h3>差價合約</h3>
			</th>
		</tr>
	</thead>
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td>
			<h3>無止損</h3>
			</td>
			<td><p><strong>合約數目 x 合約規模 x 合約價格 x 保證金比率</strong></p>

			<p>例：2筆澳元/美元合約</p>

			<p>2 x A$100,000 x 0.7690 x 0.5% = A$769 保證金要求</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>
			<h3>止損</h3>
			</td>
			<td><p><strong>(無止損倉位保證金 x 滑點指數) + (合約數目 x 每點價值 x 止損距離)</strong></p>

			<p>例：2筆 澳元/美元 合約，附15點非保證止損：</p>

			<p>($769 x 50%) + (2 x $10 x 15) = $684.50 保證金要求</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>
			<h3>保證止損</h3>
			</td>
			<td><p>以下兩個算式中較大值：</p>

			<p>1. 合約數量 x 合約尺寸 X 止損距離（按點計算）+保證止損溢價</p>

			<p>2. 合約數量 x 合約尺寸 x 合約價格 x 保證金率 (%)</p>

			<p>&nbsp;</p>

			<p>例：2筆英鎊/美元 合約，附20點止損距離，1點保證止損溢價：</p>

			<p>算式1：<strong style="text-align: center;"><span>&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="text-align: center;">(2 x $10 x 20) + (2 x $10 x 1) = $420 保證金</span></p>

			<p>算式2：<span style="text-align: center;"><span>&nbsp;</span>2 x <span>&nbsp;</span>$100,000 x 1.5500 x 0.5% = $1,550保證金</span></p>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<p>&nbsp;</p>


    

</div>

</div>
