<div class="responsive-table">

    <h3>商品保證金</h3>

<p>已設定非保證止損的差價合約倉位的保證金要求將以無止損情況下的保證金為上限（換言之若止損距離與當前價格相差較大，計算後保證金要求或會高於無止損情況下的保證金；若有此情況，保證金將會限制為相同倉位無止損情況下所需的保證金）。</p>

<table class="table-zebra-rows" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="1">
	<thead>
		<tr>
			<th scope="col" width="135"><p>&nbsp;</p>
			</th>
			<th scope="col" width="661">
			<h3>差價合約</h3>
			</th>
		</tr>
	</thead>
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td>
			<h3>無止損</h3>
			</td>
			<td><p><strong>合約數目 x 合約規模 x 價格 x 保證金比率</strong></p>

			<p>例：買入1張原油-美國原油合約：</p>

			<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">1 x $10 x 3350 x 1% = $335</span></p>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>
			<h3>止損</h3>
			</td>
			<td><p><strong>（無止損倉位保證金 x 滑點指數） + （合約數目 x 合約規模 x 止損距離）</strong></p>

			<p>例：買入1張美國原油合約，附帶非保證止損，止損距離為12點</p>

			<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 246); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">($335 x 50%) + (1 x $10 x 12) = $287.50</span> 保證金</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>
			<h3>保證止損</h3>
			</td>
			<td><p>以下兩個算式中<strong>較大值</strong>：</p>

			<p>1. 合約數量 x 合約尺寸 X 止損距離（按點計算）+保證止損溢價</p>

			<p>2. 合約數量 x 合約尺寸 x 價格 x 保證金率 (%)</p>
			&nbsp;
<p>例：買入1張美國原油合約，並於90點以外設定保證止損，保證止損溢價為4點：</p>

			<p><strong style="text-align: center;">算式1:</strong><span style="text-align: center;"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">(4 x $10) + (90 x $10) = $940</span>保證金<br style="text-align: center;">
			<strong style="text-align: center;">算式2:</strong><span style="text-align: center;"><span> </span></span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">1 x $10 x 3350 x 1% = $330 </span><span style="text-align: center;">保證金</span></p>

			<p><span style="text-align: center;">因此，保證金要求為940美元（兩者中較大的值）</span></p>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<p>&nbsp;</p>


    

